channel.desc: Teenagers, Drama 2019 Teenage girl Rocks's life changes drastically when her mother abandons her and her younger brother, putting her in charge of taking care of herself and him, which affects her decisions as she sees her friends live ordinary lives. Bukky Bakray, D'angelou Osei Kissiedu, Kosar Ali, Ruby Stokes, Tawheda Begum, Sarah Gavron, Theresa Ikoko, Claire Wilson.
